  Apart from the above action libraries, you also have a
  <strong>
   Favourites
  </strong>
  library - which is a special section of the Toolbox where you can drag actions and so keep all the ones you use the most handy - and there is also the
  <strong>
   Recently Used
  </strong>
  library, which will hold the last 5 actions that you have used:
